<br>
Let me say this again. I stole no cloak. Shadowind didnt even have a com on him at the time of this.  Let it go get on with your lives. Those of you still pissed at shadowind for something let it go. Your bound never to see him again so its wasted energy.  How would you feel if you were hounded time and time again for things you just wanted to escape from?  Dont you think its been long enough? <br>
<br>
